import {
    Wrapper,
    Card,
    FieldWrapper,
    ProgramDescHeader,
    ProgramDesc,
    SchoolDescHeader
} from './ProgramInfo.styles'


const ProgramInfo = ({programDescription, schoolDescription, schoolName}) => (
    <Wrapper>
        <FieldWrapper>
            <ProgramDescHeader>Earn Your Degree</ProgramDescHeader>
            <ProgramDesc>{programDescription}</ProgramDesc>
            <SchoolDescHeader>About {`School Name`}</SchoolDescHeader>
        </FieldWrapper>
        <Card>

        </Card>
    </Wrapper>
)

export default ProgramInfo
